# Session orchestrator

**Bootstrap hub** / **customize template** → load `.cursor/skills/bootstrap-hub/SKILL.md` + [CUSTOMIZE.md](../../CUSTOMIZE.md).

**Start work** / `/start-work` → load `.cursor/skills/session-orchestrator/SKILL.md`. You run `./scripts/*`.

**End session** / `/end-session` → load `.cursor/skills/session-end/SKILL.md`.
